<section id="Section618729">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>quotes</primary>
      <secondary>looking up by item</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>items</primary>
      <secondary>looking up by quote</secondary>
    </indexterm>Quote Lookup by Item</title>
  <para>To view Quotes by Item, select the "Quote Lookup by Item" option from
  the "Displays" menu. The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/dspQuotesByItem.png"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Quote Lookup by Item</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>
  <para>When displaying Quotes by Item, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Number</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the Item Number of the Item whose Quotes you want to
        view.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>UOM</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Inventory Unit of Measure.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Quotes</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists Quotes for the specified Item.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To the far right of the screen, the following buttons are
  available:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CLOSE</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
        desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>Right-clicking on a Quote in the Quotes list enables you to select
  from the following menu options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml" xpointer="element(rightclickEdit)"/>
    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml" xpointer="element(rightclickView)"/>
    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml" xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)"/>
  </variablelist>
</section>
